(1) Coney

Coney Island Creek,(shore)viewed eastward at West 19th Street. In the background is P.S. 80 at Neptune Ave., and West 19th Street.

July 1, 1936.

The same, from another angle.

July 1, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Coney Island Creek - East - West 19th Street - Brooklyn.
